Geez..what can I say!  Is Draft Dodger in special form or not?  We need to double the admission to two cans of ham and lima beans!<br><br>
But first let's review act one&gt;<br><br>
Tardive dyskinesia, (spelled correctly) is not a mental illness as the fake Doctor suggested.  It is a drug side effect that comes from quacks administering too much and too many antipsychotic drugs in lieu of proper counsel which causes an imbalance in dopamine and acetylcholine activity in the brain.  The result is often involuntary limb movements, chewing movements, lip smacking and sucking of the mouth.  Not a pretty thing to see nor an appropriate jest to make on a web site.<br>
His total lack of respect for women and children, the color of people's skin and socio-economic status is obvious in his raving statements.  His implied sexually predation on an innocent thirteen year old girl (my daughter) and inapproriate foul references to female anatomy is sickening and is reason for Marc Weiss to intervene once again, as he has in the past to control this mad man.<br>
He maintains that I am &quot;the most pathetic excuse for a Veteran&quot; although I was honored in the proceedings and debates of the Second Session of the 101st Congress of the United States of America for military service to my country while in Viet Nam.<br>
His blatant ignorance of Post Traumatic Stress Disorder is apparent, yet from the dim recesses of his sickness he proposes an instant cure while mocking traumatized veterans who suffer from this devastating malady.  It clearly serves to demonstrate that he (an imposter) lacks that crucial element of positive and unconditional regard that mental health professionals have for their patients and substantiates his fakery.<br>
As most bigots, those who attitudes and behaviors express intolerance for races, religions and politics, and as a truely inferior person (no achievement), he has suffered the aquisition of a &quot;Narcissitic&quot; personality disorder.  His assumed abilities, though none existent, nonetheless propel him to grandios heights in his sick fantasy world.  He actually believes that he is superior to everyone, physically, intellectually etc. when actually the opposite is the case.<br>
I am hopeful that the viewing world will gain some insight into the abuses that veterans endure each day.<br>
I find him impotent, repugnant and mostly harmless.  His filty dialogue, perversions, and total lack of propriety make him an entertaining and vulnerable target for the men of worth and intelligence who post here to discuss the impact of the Viet Nam war upon themselves, history and society.<br>
Please join me in observing this cowardly traitor, draft dodger, and idiot weave fragile webs of distraction, false statement, and foolishness to distract from his own inadequacies.  I find him to be a sad case..yet in my contempt for all that he represents..I take delight in watching him destroy himself!<br><br>
Captain Edward Ramon, RVN '66'67'69 
